<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Food Donation System</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/sidebar.css">
    <!-- Bootstrap + Font Awesome -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="text-center mb-4">
            <img src="/assets/images/logo.jpg" alt="Food Donation Logo" class="logo img-fluid" style="max-width: 150px;">
            <h1 class="mt-3 color-theme">Our Mission</h1>
            <p class="lead">Join us in making sure no food goes to waste and no one goes hungry 🍎🥗🍞</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card shadow-sm p-4 mb-5">
            <p>
                At <strong>Food Donation System</strong>, our mission is to bridge the gap between surplus and scarcity.
                Every day, tons of edible food — like fresh fruits, vegetables, bread, and meals — go to waste, 
                while millions of people go to bed hungry.
                We are committed to creating a sustainable system where donors — individuals, restaurants, and organizations — 
                can easily contribute their surplus food, ensuring it reaches those in need.
            </p>

            <p>
                Our agents work tirelessly on the ground to pick up, sort, and distribute food in the safest, most efficient manner.
                We believe in transparency, accountability, and making a positive impact on local communities.
                Together, we can fight hunger, reduce food waste, and build a better, more compassionate world.
            </p>

            <p class="fw-bold text-center">
                🍽️ Join us in making a difference. Every meal counts.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card shadow p-4">
            <h4 class="mb-3"><i class="fas fa-seedling text-success me-2"></i> With the Food Donation Web Application, Our Mission Is:</h4>
            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-leaf text-success me-2"></i> Reducing Food Waste by rescuing fresh produce, baked goods, and meals</li>
                <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-hands-helping text-primary me-2"></i> Empowering Donors and Recipients to connect effortlessly</li>
                <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-warning me-2"></i> Continuous Innovation through smart tracking and distribution tools</li>
                <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-bullhorn text-danger me-2"></i> Advocacy and Awareness to promote sustainable food systems</li>
            </ul>

            <h6 class="mt-3">
                By aligning our efforts with this mission, we aim to create a positive and lasting impact — transforming the way surplus food is managed and distributed while fostering a more equitable and sustainable future for all.
            </h6>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-dark text-light py-3 mt-5">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <p class="mb-1">&copy; 2025 Food Donation System | Built with ❤️ to feed the world</p>
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#" class="me-3 text-light"><i class="fab fa-facebook fa-lg"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="me-3 text-light"><i class="fab fa-instagram fa-lg"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="me-3 text-light"><i class="fab fa-twitter fa-lg"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="text-light"><i class="fab fa-linkedin fa-lg"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/assets/js/script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>

